title: Bush Turnpike at I-635
text: This project added two connection ramps at the interchange at Bush Turnpike and I-635, from I-635 eastbound to Bush Turnpike northbound, and Bush Turnpike southbound to I-635 westbound.

images.caption: Looking east along IH-635 at the piers for the ramp connection eastbound IH-635 to northbound Bush Turnpike.
Looking north along the Bush Turnpike (SH 161).
